Redis端口:6380

Neo4j用户名:neo4j
Neo4j密码:change-me

api-key:your-api-key
base_url="https://api.example.com/v1"
模型:gpt-5.4-mini

调用方式:
from openai import OpenAI

client = OpenAI(
    api_key="your-api-key",
    base_url="https://api.example.com/v1"
)

response = client.chat.completions.create(
    model="gpt-5.4-mini",
    messages=[{"role": "user", "content": "你好"}]
)
